text: Engina zepa is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pisaniidae. ==Description== ==Distribution== This species is distributed in the Indian Ocean along Madagascar. ==References== * Dautzenberg, Ph. (1929). Mollusques testaces marins de Madagascar. Faune des Colonies Francaises, Tome III ==External links== * Category:Pisaniidae Category:Gastropods described in 1883
title: Engina zepa
